{"tid":1477943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同我仆撚晒入黎]做實事，進攻支爆篇","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:58:33.000Z","uid":12792,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"08e9997cefa30ecfff0f135a1f5e5ccd1aef88d2","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長期抗爭攻略: 就算對家知晒我做乜，佢都冇我哋符</span></span><br />\n<br />\n支那篇<br />\n<br />\n防守性進攻<br />\n香港: <br />\n勇武繼續keep the noise. <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但畀返和理非參與空間，要有場絕對安全</span></span>，冇建樹唔緊要，透過增加參與度，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">目的係為咗令佢哋轉職<br />\n極端和理非 &gt; 和理非<br />\n和理非 &gt; 見習勇武</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武手足係防守球員，冇你哋場運動馬上完結，所以你哋係要以不被捕為前提，唔好戀戰同9打，目的係要維持運動繼續，同埋令世界注意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">加速支爆 -&gt; 支那內亂</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全軍</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">罷買非必要中資貨，抵制中資公司，中資銀行提款，罷食/買中資背景餐廳等</span></span> -&gt; 減少中資抵抗貿易戰籌碼<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">提款usd衝擊聯匯</span>，hkma要用usd 維持聯匯。另一方面，銀行儲備減少。both加重銀行壓力令支那冇得搶香港USD(發行人債)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">低質支那民，上了天堂回不了地面</span>，冇錢(唯一驕傲)，就會blame政府，小小trigger就會內亂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那義討軍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">參軍隊(要真hacker高手，最好係外國巴絲，帝吧征討軍俾我好大鼓舞)</span><br />\n1. 無差別參軍(<span style=\"color: gold;\">癱瘓同混亂支那募兵系統</span>，令佢地招募真係想參軍ge都用多d時間fc bg check)<br />\n2. 無差別hack真支那撚acct 開post 8964&lt;&lt;呢個係疑兵。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">信:捉人，民反; 不信: unlock支那言論自由</span><br />\n真兵: <span style=\"color: red;\">再無差別hack真支那撚acct 以其他原因(eg 武漢焚化爐、成都霧霾事件、京A88519 etc)開潑火post。</span>先從二線城市開波，之後三線，最後一線，明點解嘅人就會明<br />\n(大家要了解多d支那新聞同社會情況)<br />\n公安同武警一定會alert, 然後捉人，佢地係寧願捉錯人都唔放生一個，然後結果係百姓抗議造反<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">配合加速支爆，持續地做，睇佢地仲可唔可以1秒到香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中共岀武警: 百姓真反<br />\n唔岀: 支那民都可能因為試過咁都冇事，unlock左佢地言論自由呢個禁忌，我哋變相教育左佢哋自由民主</span><br />\nBe water: 疑兵真兵互相crossover，隨時做，又隨時停，be safe 不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼隊</span></span><br />\n如果捉到鬼(both港鬼/支那鬼)，8964影相(多張)再公安局舉報。<span style=\"color: red;\">未完，半年後拎另一張相再舉報一次</span>，如是者得閒記得又舉報下，<span style=\"color: pink;\">等佢煩都煩一世，體會一下活在恐懼下滋味。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣隊</span></span><br />\n1. 努力黃化可接觸支那民，宣揚民主自由<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">配合參軍隊，潑火支那發大支那社會衝突</span>(京a88159) ，對象係支那民，先從二線城市開波，之後三線，最後一線<br />\n大家自己發揮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港篇</span></span><br />\n分化差佬同佢哋上級係冇用，因為佢哋一樣屌上級，但係怕冇咗份工，供唔到樓，養唔到屋企，所以乜都照做<br />\n所以要繼續做禍必及妻(sor未突破到，唔想搞細路)<br />\n1. 分化狗同狗嫂 (文宣: 狗嫂綠帽，狗叫免費雞<br />\n2. 分化狗嫂同佢親朋好友 (狗嫂一定冇狗咁捱得，因為自己唔係嗰份工，冇落過場)，從而狗嫂比壓力狗 (eg. 文宣爭人錢etc)<br />\n自由發揮<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港戰術篇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">戰略篇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">反破解對家連橫我地ge 合縱(而家情況根本就係春秋戰國合縱連橫)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">利用香港嘅國際金融地位，主導外國的對華態度同戰略，成為貿易戰第三方勢力</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">真民主香港人權約章的信念 (誠哥已經代勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">無政府狀態下高人民素質社會的運作</span><br />\nEtc<br />\n有機會再分享<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭要保持唔同形式，要成日變，因為香港人實在太貪新鮮感同善忘</span></span>，日日都打，對成件事只係害多於利，因為一個和理非場，一set路障，就算冇打，極端和理非都會從此home office，全民運動不應只滿足鍾意打嘅一班人，一句不割蓆但係不出席，就已經判定左運動去到終結。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">切勿home office !! </span><br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲要不缺席</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人加油💪🏼<br />\n<br />\n我真係好希望贏㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">背後理念同邏輯，睇埋呢個pls</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">轉台開 [極重要]拆解劉sir 大招新戰略 + 運動方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470963\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470963</a></span>"},{"pid":"7af762bd5284c1df305cf9307bd3f58b816e61ed","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"因果由國 容港治己 義憤民誠"},{"pid":"b004603852497ef0d1caa2a8057a9ddec04ce3a0","tid":1477943,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"Push, 各司其職！大家努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f2426729b282eea8957d3eae487f11fcdc48ac","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b004603852497ef0d1caa2a8057a9ddec04ce3a0","tid":1477943,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"Push, 各司其職！大家努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"因果由國 容港治己！<br />\n818"},{"pid":"ced08400de4dcbfb7ea01545ea60b42cde05a611","tid":1477943,"uid":60881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"因果由國<br />\n容港治己<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命 <br />\n<br />\n818 我地要用人數塞爆佢地把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0235702ef05a87dcb35a3c10c76fc31a64b32772","tid":1477943,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>和理非係時候要進化喇! 818 同步搞! 後備持久戰plan! </strong><br />\n<br />\n［推上熱門！！！］全港新戰略‐和理非『節奏抗爭』每日9點準時敲擊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475606</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uybaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uybaW.jpg&h=ddfac6a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"217f8f1beef9b41435f6b3794ed1b9b650e09492","tid":1477943,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSD-Challenge-103297651036526%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=c663b536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群香港人，熱血自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n我們現正受到中國黨國體系的打壓，我們不希望在銀行的存款成為中資企業的貸款，助紂為虐；我們亦不相信港共政權並沒有透過外匯基金持有大量人民幣資產。<br />\n<br />\n對於一個連市民性命安危都無法保障的政府，我們不認為他們有能力捍衛龐大的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們發起USD Challenge。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n「接受挑戰者，請到銀行或找換店換取至少1000蚊美元現鈔，拍照上傳至社交媒體，同時附上此段文字並標籤三名好友，向他們發起挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers embracing freedom and democracy.<br />\n<br />\nWe are currently oppressed by the China party state system. We don&rsquo;t want our deposits in bank becomes loans for Chinese enterprises. Such action is assisting tyrant to act brutally. Also, we don&rsquo;t believe that the communist regime in Hong Kong doesn&rsquo;t hold large portion of RMB assets through Exchange Funds. <br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t think that the Government is able to defend the huge Linked Exchange Rate System because the Government cannot even protect citizens&rsquo; lives.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, we launch USD Challenge.<br />\n<br />\nThe flow is as followed:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who accept the challenge, please go to banks or exchange stores, get at least $1000 USD cash, take a photo and upload to any social media. At the same time, attach this paragraph, tag three friends and challenge them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4a791e51256856b85403fd8bdbf436f8138d2a31","tid":1477943,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSD-Challenge-103297651036526%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=c663b536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群香港人，熱愛自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n我們現正受到中國黨國體系的打壓，我們不希望在銀行的存款成為中資企業的貸款，助紂為虐；我們亦不相信港共政權並沒有透過外匯基金持有大量人民幣資產。<br />\n<br />\n對於一個連市民性命安危都無法保障的政府，我們不認為他們有能力捍衛龐大的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們發起USD Challenge。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n「接受挑戰者，請到銀行或找換店換取至少1000蚊美元現鈔，拍照上傳至社交媒體，同時附上此段文字並標籤三名好友，向他們發起挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers embracing freedom and democracy.<br />\n<br />\nWe are currently oppressed by the China party state system. We don&rsquo;t want our deposits in bank becomes loans for Chinese enterprises. Such action is assisting tyrant to act brutally. Also, we don&rsquo;t believe that the communist regime in Hong Kong doesn&rsquo;t hold large portion of RMB assets through Exchange Funds. <br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t think that the Government is able to defend the huge Linked Exchange Rate System because the Government cannot even protect citizens&rsquo; lives.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, we launch USD Challenge.<br />\n<br />\nThe flow is as followed:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who accept the challenge, please go to banks or exchange stores, get at least $1000 USD cash, take a photo and upload to any social media. At the same time, attach this paragraph, tag three friends and challenge them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"3fd7b936c59a1a0f6c420c7225dfa33ab64944f5","tid":1477943,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime