normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<br />\n⒉疑插贜竹枝 <strong>造偽證</strong> 誣陷被捕者、被捕者警處放出後 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>腦出血</strong></span>、<br />\n⒊地鐡<strong>站內 水平發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣、<br />\n⒋警<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">喬裝示威者 發動衝擊</span></strong>、<br />\n⒌普通話<strong>軍人 多處滲透</strong>武統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<br />\n⒍<strong>一米內行刑 掃射</strong>胡椒彈槍、險釀電梯<strong>人踩人</strong>、<br />\n⒎<strong>縱容黑幫</strong>橫行 毆打記者路人、皮肉剝離血肉模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n⒏濫暴<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">痛毆 重創被捕者</span></strong> 打掉門牙、<br />\n    今證實周日被捕人士移送羅湖文錦渡後，<span style=\"color: orange;\">各有骨折、斷手、斷背、頸椎移位</span>傷勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n⒐屋村<strong>老人民居範圍 發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣<br />\n１０. 殘害救護員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<strong>救護舉旗警告</strong> 尖沙咀<strong>阻礙救援</strong> 違反國際人道法 屬嚴重刑事罪行</span>"},{"pid":"44db1fb263057cba10a7952cb16a9279c397449a","tid":1477943,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">向內反攻內地文宣 向外爭取各國支援<br />\n小心冷靜 手機紀錄身邊所有突發場面<br />\n影低可疑特務去向 <span style=\"color: red;\">眾口鑠金 積毀銷骨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分化</span> 保持警覺</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>關鍵詞：普世價值、公關風暴、<br />\n                    民意輿論、借力打力</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心暗黑兵法劇本：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n內耗：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>內部分化</strong></span>示威者、<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">酷刑威嚇</span></strong>被捕人士、<br />\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨阻<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">抗爭之風蔓延內陸</span></strong>、<br />\n逐步<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">暴力鎮壓 拘捕</span></strong>前線瓦解、<br />\n文宣<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">抹黑 嫁禍 插贜</span></strong>示威者、<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暗殺</span></strong>第一滴血 逆轉民意 國際譴責、<br />\n人民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、<br />\n中立派賺錢派 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">政治疲勞</span></strong>、<br />\n鼓吹經濟下滑 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、<br />\n拖延分散擊破 學季始開、<br />\n雨傘結局 清算開始<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歌聲招降大法 <br />\n「做人要有公關」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">擁抱自由</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"9ef31d59a1edae8a41ed1703e11766a5a11a04c1","tid":1477943,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"好一句不缺席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414bda510f072d0d1fad9495a1bb4bff6d04856f","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ef31d59a1edae8a41ed1703e11766a5a11a04c1","tid":1477943,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"好一句不缺席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打，不缺席同不割蓆同樣重要"},{"pid":"86c5873924ab469e97401a99622af73227f77f2e","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"aee87568bd3f4368d7f56ed33b85a010abb1aef5","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"7a5b0791318c4c7b525989cc1e80f99f4c920802","tid":1477943,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"很好的建議<br />\n推"},{"pid":"6a188f3c89945aff2b5fb877836edd3ad6dafe36","tid":1477943,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a5b0791318c4c7b525989cc1e80f99f4c920802","tid":1477943,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor